HEADWORD: Pumpage
<hw>Pump"age</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>That which is raised
by pumps, or the work done by pumps.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The <qex>pumpage</qex> last year amounted to . . . gallons.</q>
<rj><qau>Sci. Amer.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

